          <label class="flex items-start p-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-purple-400 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="A" data-correct="B" class="mt-1">
            <span class="ml-3"><strong>A.</strong> Asignar a cada niño/a el rincón donde debe jugar</span>
          </label>

          <label class="flex items-start p-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-purple-400 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="B" data-correct="B" class="mt-1">
            <span class="ml-3"><strong>B.</strong> Preguntar '¿qué te gustaría hacer hoy?' y mostrar las opciones disponibles</span>
          </label>

          <label class="flex items-start p-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-purple-400 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="C" data-correct="B" class="mt-1">
            <span class="ml-3"><strong>C.</strong> Organizar un juego dirigido para todo el grupo</span>
          </label>

          <label class="flex items-start p-3 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-purple-400 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="D" data-correct="B" class="mt-1">
